
** Installing Bzr

*** ubuntu

  - sudo apt-get install python2.5-dev

*** install

  - sudo python setup.py install

  http://bazaar-vcs.org/InstallationFaq

** Additional Packages

  - pycrypto-2.0.1.tar.gz
  - paramiko-1.7.5.zip

** Emacs

  http://bzr.savannah.gnu.org/r/emacs/trunk/

** Commands

*** init

The first command should be "init".

*** pull

  --overwrite

  bzr pull sftp://maierh@ate/~/build/bzr/trunk

The sftp method needs paramiko module and the python-devel package.

